# Cursor Agent Rules — HW5 ECG/HRV Analysis

## CRITICAL: Notebook Protection
- NEVER run `scripts/build_notebooks.py` — it overwrites ALL notebooks and destroys manual edits.
- NEVER execute any script that batch-writes to `notebooks/*.ipynb`.
- NEVER use `nbformat.write()` to overwrite an existing notebook file.
- NEVER run `python -c` or inline scripts that write complete notebook JSON.
- Before modifying any notebook, ALWAYS ask the user for confirmation.
- Prefer editing individual cells rather than rewriting entire notebooks.

## Commit Discipline
- After making changes, always remind the user to commit.
- Never run `git add -A` or `git add .` — always add specific files by name.

## Figure Convention
- Figures use `PL.save_figure(fig, "nbXX_figYY_description.pdf")`.
- FIG_DIR = `outputs/figures`.
